    <ac:image>
        <ri:attachment ri:filename="image-2026-7-6_11-17-24.png" />
    </ac:image>
</p>
<p>When ULT is entered for any line item by Agent/Customer and the return quantity of the line is greater than
    <strong>1</strong>, the system will automatically change the return quantity to <strong>1</strong> by default. If
    the user wants to process the particular MM having a line for multiple quantity, the user will then need to add
