</p>
<p>
    <ac:image>
        <ri:attachment ri:filename="image-2026-7-6_11-17-40.png" />
    </ac:image>
</p>
<ul>
    <li>After clicking the <strong>Warranty Entitlement Check</strong> button, the system will check if the return
        quantity has changed after entering the ULT for any line item having Return Qty &gt; 1.</li>
    <li>If Return Quantity has changed after entering the ULT, a pop-up window will appear, allowing the user to add
        ULTs for the remaining quantity using the <strong>bulk upload</strong> option.</li>
</ul>
<p>
