        <ri:attachment ri:filename="image-2026-7-6_11-17-52.png" />
    </ac:image>
</p>
<ul>
    <li>If the user doesn't want to add ULTs for the remaining quantity, he can click <strong>Proceed without New
            Lines</strong> to skip this step. The system will perform the Warranty validations for existing lines and
        display the result.</li>
    <li>If the user wants to add more lines for any MM which had quantity &gt; 1 before giving ULT, he has to provide
        ULTs for the remaining quantity using the process below.</li>
</ul>
<p>
    <strong>Downloading the ULT Template</strong>
</p>
<ul>
    <li>User should download the template file by clicking <strong>Download Template</strong>. A CSV file will be
        downloaded, which contains three columns:</li>
</ul>
