    </ac:image>
</p>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>MM</strong>: This is the product name.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>ULT</strong>: This is the unique identifier for the product.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Line Identifier</strong>: This is used to match the data to the correct line item (Backend purpose)
    </li>
</ul>
<ac:structured-macro ac:macro-id="e4b0d7db-7f59-4fef-813f-ec650faaf332" ac:name="info" ac:schema-version="1">
    <ac:parameter ac:name="title">Important</ac:parameter>
    <ac:rich-text-body>
        <p>Do not change any column headers, add or delete rows, or modify existing data in the template. You only need
            to fill in the ULT for each MM item.</p>
