</ac:structured-macro>
<p>
    <strong>Uploading the ULT File</strong>
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Once the user has added the ULTs required for additional lines, the user should upload the file by clicking
        <strong>Upload Files</strong>. The system will check the file for the following:
    </li>
</ul>
<p>
    <ac:image>
        <ri:attachment ri:filename="image-2026-7-6_11-18-18.png" />
    </ac:image>
</p>
<ol>
    <li>No changes to the column headers.</li>
    <li>No new rows added or existing rows deleted/modified.</li>
    <li>Each ULT must be filled out, with a length between 6 to 40 characters, and no duplicates allowed.</li>
</ol>
<ul>
    <li>If there are any errors, they will be shown on the screen. User can download the error file, make corrections,
        and upload it again.</li>
</ul>
<p>
    <ac:image>
        <ri:attachment ri:filename="image-2026-7-6_11-18-32.png" />
    </ac:image>
</p>
<p>
    <strong>Validation and Next Steps</strong>
</p>
<ul>
    <li>If the file is correct, the system will upload it successfully. After clicking <strong>Validate</strong>, new
        lines will be added to the table, and the system will perform further checks, such as making sure there are no
